{"tid":1335782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日請發揮BE WATER的精神","createTime":"2019-07-20T16:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T06:24:14.000Z","uid":94771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8383fd20dac454c8a686687c7119308d23ce2ccb","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:10:04.000Z","msg":"佢迫民陣終點SET係灣仔一定有古怪<br />\n聽日發現有古怪 立即散去 去西環又好 中環個個都好 唔好守係灣仔<br />\n警犬會放不反對通知書到23:59 <br />\n一定係因為覺得遊行唔會去到23:59 應該直接宣佈非法集會 取消你個不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n始終真係唔知警犬點佈置<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警犬有報導(蘋果日報)全出5000 PTU警力 即係一散走 佢地無多餘的犬力去應對</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好諗住有守的慨念 BE WATER </span></strong><br />\n5000PTU 幾乎係示威者應付唔到 請記得大部份都係和理非<br />\n所以灣仔發生衝突/衝擊係極其不智 <br />\n<br />\n如果想煲高遊行人數 可以考慮唔好咁快行動<br />\n勇武一行動 後續的和理非就唔敢出來 係屋企做軍帥算 <br />\n7.1因為太早作出衝擊行動 好多和理非係卻步佐 唔係想同勇武割席係擔心有危險而唔出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依個只係建議 當然幾時行動我就相信你地有你地的智慧決定</span></strong>"},{"pid":"531c40af3de4ae0e8380b6ccfd357061002a6b13","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86392050433b3acb1bb2200b9cfa93091b2c37d3","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d2283d791878757f7bb89bdbd6ce1255574225","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"十連開始<br />\n1"},{"pid":"635a0117f21d667bfad5db0b3f13d24be3c4abaf","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"十連開始<br />\n2"},{"pid":"4575c3541bbc816f174dfe3a9fe5ccd93aea23a9","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"十連開始<br />\n3"},{"pid":"d65761fc86e2754c99ca40c96ebe1ad0a00526fe","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"十連開始<br />\n4"},{"pid":"8f0a51fe915922a69f9b36477334fa8c5a698d4a","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"十連開始<br />\n5"},{"pid":"972cb8b2d917d2ef6bc7200ec59b0b137e4f4ae9","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"十連開始<br />\n6"},{"pid":"8836e84a0c7d58063620c9134bd47daac51ee19e","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eec528920e344615448cf50c15231fb774e163","tid":1335782,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"做足準備 但不設行動框架<br />\n大家現場執生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8fe7e84a4b391c904ed1f9c92b09939ac23bb3","tid":1335782,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}